\c 10
\s Ukufa kukaSawuli lamadodana akhe
\p
\v 1 AmaFilisti asesilwa emelene loIsrayeli; lamadoda akoIsrayeli abaleka phambi kwamaFilisti, awa abulawa entabeni yeGilibowa\x + 1 Sam. 31.1-13.\x*.
\v 2 AmaFilisti asenamathela ngemva kukaSawuli langemva kwamadodana akhe; amaFilisti atshaya uJonathani loAbinadaba loMaliki-Shuwa, amadodana kaSawuli.
\v 3 Impi yasisiba nzima imelene loSawuli; abatshoka ngamadandili basebemfica; waselinyazwa ngabatshoki.
\v 4 USawuli wasesithi kumthwali wezikhali zakhe: Hwatsha inkemba yakho, ungigwaze ngayo, hlezi laba abangasokanga bafike, badlale kubi ngami. Kodwa umthwali wezikhali zakhe kavumanga, ngoba wesaba kakhulu. USawuli wasethatha inkemba, wa\add zi\add*wisela phezu kwayo.
\v 5 Lapho umthwali wezikhali zakhe ebona ukuthi uSawuli u\add se\add*file, laye wa\add zi\add*wisela phezu kwenkemba, wafa.
\v 6 Wafa-ke uSawuli, lamadodana akhe amathathu, lendlu yakhe yonke; bafa ndawonye\x + 1 Sam. 31.6.\x*.
\v 7 Kwathi wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli ayesesigodini ebona ukuthi abalekile, lokuthi uSawuli lamadodana akhe bafile, atshiya imizi yawo, abaleka; amaFilisti asefika, ahlala kiyo\x + 1 Sam. 31.7.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Kwasekusithi kusisa lapho amaFilisti efika ukuhlubula ababuleweyo, afica uSawuli lamadodana akhe bewile entabeni yeGilibowa.
\v 9 Amhlubula, athatha ikhanda lakhe lezikhali zakhe, athumela elizweni lamaFilisti inhlangothi zonke, ukumemezela imibiko ezithombeni zawo lebantwini\x + 1 Sam. 31.9.\x*.
\v 10 Asebeka izikhali zakhe endlini yabonkulunkulu bawo, abethela ukhakhayi lwakhe endlini kaDagoni\x + 1 Sam. 31.10.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Kwathi iJabeshi-Gileyadi yonke isizwile konke amaFilisti akwenze kuSawuli,
\v 12 wonke amaqhawe asuka, athatha isidumbu sikaSawuli lezidumbu zamadodana akhe, aziletha eJabeshi, angcwaba amathambo abo ngaphansi kwesihlahla \w se-okhi\w** eJabeshi, azila ukudla insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + 1 Sam. 31.13.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Ngakho uSawuli wafa ngenxa yesiphambeko sakhe aphambuka ngaso emelene leN\nd kosi\nd*, emelene lelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ayengaligcinanga\x + 1 Sam. 13.13. 15.23.\x*, njalo langokubuza koledlozi ukudinga \add kuye\x + 1 Sam. 28.7.\x*\add*,
\v 14 njalo kakudinganga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1 Sam. 28.6.\x*. Ngakho yambulala, yaguqulela umbuso kuDavida indodana kaJese\x + 12.23. 1 Sam. 15.28. 2 Sam. 3.9,10.\x*.
